creator: Sinecloud
descriptionHtml:
Paris Orly Airport, is an international airport located partially in Orly and partially in Villeneuve-le-Roi, 13 km south of Paris, France. It serves as a secondary hub for domestic and overseas territories flights of Air France and as the homebase for Transavia France.

This app provides in-depth information for ORY airport.

App features :
- Comprehensive airport information.
- Live arrival/departure boards with flight tracker (including map).
- World Clock : Set up a world clock with your selection of cities.
- Currency Converter : Live exchange rates and converter, supports currencies from every country.
- My Trips : Manage all your flight trips, track your flight, web check-in, share trip details.
- Packing checklist : Keep track of things to pack for your next trip.
- Next flight : Find and book the next available flight from Paris.
- Emergency Numbers : Added emergency numbers for France.
descriptionShort: Paris Orly Airport (ORY) information and flight tracker
